Jeff Rawle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Rawle 0 Jeffrey Alan Rawle (born 20 July 1951) is a British actor, known for playing the long-suffering George Dent in the news-gathering sitcom Drop the Dead Donkey. He also played Silas Blissett in Hollyoaks from December 2010 until 2012. Rawle returned to Hollyoaks in 2016.
